```

Docs UI: [http://localhost:8081/docs](http://localhost:8081/docs)

### Main Commands

- `make generate` — generate proto/openapi artifacts
- `make mocks` — generate mocks into `test/mock`
- `make lint`
- `make test`
- `make build`
- `make run`
